# ==(_:_:)

**Operator**

Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether two values are equal.

## Declaration

```swift
static func == (lhs: PKDisbursementError, rhs: PKDisbursementError) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **lhs**: A value to compare.
- **rhs**: Another value to compare.

## Return Value

Returns [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/true] if the values are equal; otherwise [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/false].
